Ingredients


Noodles:

Egg noodles, or
Rice noodles (gluten free option)



Sauce:

Light soy sauce
Dark soy sauce
Sesame oil
Honey
Oyster sauce (optional)
White pepper
Vegetable stock powder
Salt


Vegetables:

Carrot
Beans
Mushroom
Broccoli
Pok choy
Bean sprouts
Spring onion
Method
Boil noodles (do not over cook)
Mix all items in the bowl for sauce
Stir fry vegetables
Add noodles and sauce and mix




